subject: Lacrosse
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Fielding five fifth-year seniors who were given an extra year of eligibility after a scandal-shortened 2006 season, Duke’s lacrosse team is the overwhelming favorite in the N.C.A.A. tournament.
